docreader.list

Class SublistManager.FakeListManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • docreader.list.SublistManager.FakeListManager
  • Enclosing class:
    SublistManager

    private static final class SublistManager.FakeListManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles paragraphs which are technically not in a list but visually look like a list member
    i.e. "1.2.3 I pretend to be a list item" as the paragraph text

    Note: Limitations of this implementation:

    1. Paragraphs which do not conform to the above pattern but need to be considered as a list paragraph, nevertheless, need to be coded in here explicitly
    2. We assume all numberTexts of the paragraphs start at the root level (i.e. each time we come across a new numberText pattern we start a new base list)
